Post-Miocene tectonics of the Northern Calcareous Alps.

Szczygieł J(1)(2), Baroň I(3), Melichar R(4), Plan L(5), Mitrović-Woodell I(6), 
Kaminsky E(7), Scholz D(8), Grasemann B(6).

Author information:
(1)Department of Geology, University of Vienna, Vienna, Austria. 
jacek.szczygiel@us.edu.pl.
(2)Institute of Earth Sciences, University of Silesia, Sosnowiec, Poland. 
jacek.szczygiel@us.edu.pl.
(3)Institute of Rock Structure and Mechanics, The Czech Academy of Sciences, 
