The global, regional, and national burden of benign prostatic hyperplasia in 204 
countries and territories from 2000 to 2019: a systematic analysis for the 
Global Burden of Disease Study 2019.

GBD 2019 Benign Prostatic Hyperplasia Collaborators.

Collaborators: Awedew AF, Han H, Abbasi B, Abbasi-Kangevari M, Ahmed MB, 
Almidani O, Amini E, Arabloo J, Argaw AM, Athari SS, Atlaw D, Banach M, Barrow 
A, Bhagavathula AS, Bhojaraja VS, Bikbov B, Bodicha BBA, Butt NS, Caetano Dos 
